5 June 2019 Cabinet will hold its Lekgotla on the 12-14 June 2019 at Sefako Makgatho Presidential Guest House in Pretoria. Members of the media are advised that there will be a  photo opportunity and remarks on the first day of the meeting, 12 June 2019. Journalists wishing to cover the photo-opportunity and remarks are requested to submit their details by 15h00, Friday, 07 June 2019  to pheliswa@gcis.gov.za using the template below. NAME SURNAME ORGANISATION FUNCTION ID OR PASSPORT NUMBER CONTACT NUMBER EMAIL ADDRESS                             NB: Access to the venue will only be granted to those who have submitted the required details. Enquiries:Phumla WilliamsGCIS Acting Director-GeneralCell: 083 501 0139